# 8.7 Service Area Pages

Agar business multiple cities me service deta hai to har city ke liye alag page banana best practice hai.

Example:

```text
/Fire-Extinguisher-Mumbai

/Fire-Extinguisher-Virar

/Fire-Extinguisher-Vasai

/Fire-Extinguisher-Thane

/Fire-Extinguisher-Navi-Mumbai
```

Har page ka content unique hona chahiye.

