# 8.9 Customer Reviews

Reviews Local SEO ka bahut important ranking factor hain.

Google positive aur genuine reviews ko importance deta hai.

Best Practices:

* Happy Customers se review maango.
* Har review ka reply do.
* Fake reviews avoid karo.

Example:

⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

> "Excellent Fire Safety Service. Highly Recommended."

